org.apache.giraph.graph

类 GraphMapper<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,M extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Mapper<Object,Object,Object,Object>
      • org.apache.giraph.graph.GraphMapper<I,V,E,M>
  • 类型参数:
    I - Vertex id
    V - Vertex data
    E - Edge data
    M - Message data

    public class GraphMapper<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,M extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Mapper<Object,Object,Object,Object>
    This mapper that will execute the BSP graph tasks alloted to this worker. All tasks will be performed by calling the GraphTaskManager object managed by this GraphMapper wrapper classs. Since this mapper will not be passing data by key-value pairs through the MR framework, the Mapper parameter types are irrelevant, and set to Object type.
